al/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係串緊嗰啲入嚟講句垃圾就走嘅人咋喎<br />\n你唔係連依啲人都撐呀嘛？<br />\n唔洗急，等多陣一定有依啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cbd3496aab21052a20f5ca2d692aab03ce53ba","tid":170603,"uid":2674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都學緊日本<br />\n好撚多費要交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁講<br />\n講交稅香港真係小兒科"},{"pid":"211573cfe1b01090ad844611f5b4cef2398f1d2a","tid":170603,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada225fcf810d2c94186a1bc2f3371d08efba173","tid":170603,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港都學緊日本<br />\n好撚多費要交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁講<br />\n講交稅香港真係小兒科</blockquote><br />\n交比政府少姐<br />\n但交比地產商個筆仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dda44f4215e75edc774d094f388ae7aa5b183d","tid":170603,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港都學緊日本<br />\n好撚多費要交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁講<br />\n講交稅香港真係小兒科</blockquote><br />\n交比政府少姐<br />\n但交比地產商個筆仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港表面交得少咋，實際你地交左幾多地稅比地產黨，依家買野仲貴過日本呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd68bc3e824caa101da4573339d44e966d55d69","tid":170603,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>